comments: Mitchell (UTA) cleanly dislodges the ball from Middleton (MIL).

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Holiday (MIL) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to Utah.

Carter (MIL) moves forward into Conley's (UTA) body and initiates contact as he defends the shot attempt.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) is already in O'Neale's (UTA) path and does not deliver contact as he turns away to disengage.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: After the deflection by Gobert (UTA), Antetokounmpo (MIL) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball touches the shot clock.  Possession is correctly awarded to Utah.
Gobert (UTA) is already in Holiday's (MIL) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Holiday (MIL) contests Mitchell's (UTA) driving shot attempt and marginal contact occurs after Mitchell has released his shot attempt.
Gobert (UTA) makes contact with Middleton's (MIL) arm/wrist as he moves forward into Middleton and the contact affects Middleton's ability to secure the rebound.
Mitchell (UTA) pulls Middleton's (MIL) jersey away from his body and affects his FOM in transition.
Holiday (MIL) cleanly deflects the ball away from Mitchell (UTA).
Gobert (UTA) legally contests Matthews' (MIL) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Mitchell (UTA) briefly grasps Antetokounmpo's (MIL) shorts with his right hand as he dislodges the ball from Antetokounmpo with his left hand.
Gobert (UTA) pulls Antetokounmpo's (MIL) jersey away from his body during the inbound and impedes his ability to disengage.
O'Neale (UTA) jumps vertically as he defends the inbound pass, and the marginal contact is caused by Antetokounmpo (MIL) as he moves towards the rim.
Correctly called 24 second violation.
Middleton (MIL) swipes his hand down and makes contact with Gobert's (UTA) arm as he defends the shot near the rim.
Mitchell (UTA) commits a take foul on Carter (MIL).
After the initial contact, Gobert (UTA) continues to re-establish himself in Holiday's (MIL) path and delivers contact with his arm extended.
O'Neale (UTA) commits a take foul on Antetokounmpo (MIL).
Gobert (UTA) is already in Matthews' (MIL) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
